            <list>
               <point>
                  <num>(a)</num>
                  <p>the identity of the controller referred to in Article 41(4), including his contact details;</p>
               </point>
               <point>
                  <num>(b)</num>
                  <p>the purposes for which the data will be processed within the VIS;</p>
               </point>
               <point>
                  <num>(c)</num>
                  <p>the categories of recipients of the data, including the authorities referred to in Article 3;</p>
               </point>
               <point>
                  <num>(d)</num>
                  <p>the data retention period;</p>
               </point>
               <point>
                  <num>(e)</num>
                  <p>that the collection of the data is mandatory for the examination of the application;</p>
               </point>
               <point>
                  <num>(f)</num>
